WEBVTT

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:05.040
Good morning, everybody. Thank you for

00:00:02.560 --> 00:00:08.080
joining us again today. We're going

00:00:05.040 --> 00:00:10.400
to pray, of course, like we always do.

00:00:08.080 --> 00:00:12.400
I want to go over some of the

00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:14.240
things the Lord showed us yesterday in

00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:16.480
prayer, and I feel the urgency of the

00:00:14.240 --> 00:00:19.119
hour. First off, I want to say thank you

00:00:16.480 --> 00:00:20.320
all for joining me, but we have a lot

00:00:19.119 --> 00:00:22.320
of work to do. We're going to pray for

00:00:20.320 --> 00:00:24.160
the nation and for

00:00:22.320 --> 00:00:26.000
President Trump and his safety. We'll

00:00:24.160 --> 00:00:28.160
pray for all the things the Lord has shown

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:29.519
us, and we'll

00:00:28.160 --> 00:00:30.800
just go over some of the things that

00:00:29.519 --> 00:00:35.160
the Lord showed us

00:00:30.800 --> 00:00:35.160
yesterday. But

00:00:35.600 --> 00:00:39.840
yesterday,

00:00:37.840 --> 00:00:41.360
just the pulse of everything, I've never

00:00:39.840 --> 00:00:42.719
seen it like this before. And that's why

00:00:41.360 --> 00:00:44.160
I thought it was really cool

00:00:42.719 --> 00:00:46.879
because whenever the Lord was showing me

00:00:44.160 --> 00:00:49.038
in the spirit, I saw a wall, a watchman's

00:00:46.879 --> 00:00:51.839
wall. I was on the wall,

00:00:49.039 --> 00:00:54.640
and it was a beautiful stone wall.

00:00:51.840 --> 00:00:57.440
It wasn't like

00:00:54.640 --> 00:01:00.320
bricks; it was like rock. And I was on

00:00:57.440 --> 00:01:03.519
this rock, and I was looking and there were

00:01:00.320 --> 00:01:06.159
portals that looked like

00:01:03.520 --> 00:01:09.520
wormholes. The only way I can describe

00:01:06.159 --> 00:01:12.799
it to you is like yellow, bright

00:01:09.520 --> 00:01:15.039
light portals, but there were

00:01:12.799 --> 00:01:17.040
one, two, three, four, and they went

00:01:15.040 --> 00:01:19.439
down the line. And the Lord said, "You

00:01:17.040 --> 00:01:22.240
can pick and choose. Every one of these

00:01:19.439 --> 00:01:26.158
right now is vital to pray over. I have

00:01:22.240 --> 00:01:28.320
much to show you

00:01:26.159 --> 00:01:30.320
because of what's happening with the

00:01:28.320 --> 00:01:32.559
urgency of the hour."If you don't

00:01:30.320 --> 00:01:34.559
know, I think you'd have to have your

00:01:32.560 --> 00:01:36.320
wood completely wet to not realize that

00:01:34.560 --> 00:01:37.840
Jesus is coming.

00:01:36.320 --> 00:01:39.600
He's coming. That's what I'm trying

00:01:37.840 --> 00:01:41.520
to tell y'all. He is coming. Jesus is

00:01:39.600 --> 00:01:43.600
coming. And your wood would have to be

00:01:41.520 --> 00:01:45.039
completely wet for you not to see it.

00:01:43.600 --> 00:01:47.520
That's what I'm trying to say. Did I

00:01:45.040 --> 00:01:49.680
butcher that? I probably did, didn't I?

00:01:47.520 --> 00:01:52.560
But I'm trying to tell you that it's

00:01:49.680 --> 00:01:55.280
time to wake up. And so I saw the wall,

00:01:52.560 --> 00:01:57.840
and every single one of the

00:01:55.280 --> 00:02:00.640
portals that were up on this wall was

00:01:57.840 --> 00:02:02.719
an urgency in

00:02:00.640 --> 00:02:04.479
the spirit realm to pray over. And he

00:02:02.719 --> 00:02:06.559
said, "You can pick and choose today

00:02:04.479 --> 00:02:09.119
which one you want to go down."And he's

00:02:06.560 --> 00:02:11.039
never given me that option before.

00:02:09.119 --> 00:02:13.440
So I was kind of scattered because I was

00:02:11.038 --> 00:02:14.720
like, "Well, which one is vital to you?

00:02:13.440 --> 00:02:17.920
Which one do you want?"Every one of

00:02:14.720 --> 00:02:19.920
these is a necessity for

00:02:17.920 --> 00:02:22.799
where we are right now. This is very—and

00:02:19.920 --> 00:02:25.200
I could see, and this is cool as

00:02:39.920 --> 00:02:44.640
it was panning before my eyes, I could see pictures like you would see on a real-life reel on YouTube. It was panning before my eyes.

00:02:41.519 --> 00:02:47.680
The screen looked like a

00:02:44.640 --> 00:02:50.480
live movie, and in every single one of

00:02:47.680 --> 00:02:53.120
them, I could see terrorist attacks,

00:02:50.480 --> 00:02:55.760
the finances of the nation,

00:02:53.120 --> 00:02:57.760
President Trump's health, so many

00:02:55.760 --> 00:02:59.200
different things going down, and every

00:02:57.760 --> 00:03:00.560
single one of them is vital.

00:03:00.560 --> 00:03:04.239
After I walked up to the wall, I

00:03:02.480 --> 00:03:06.799
just went, "Well, I'll just scattershot

00:03:04.239 --> 00:03:08.319
this thing.

00:03:06.800 --> 00:03:09.680
We'll pray into all of them."So we

00:03:08.319 --> 00:03:11.599
prayed for a long time, and I said, "I'm

00:03:09.680 --> 00:03:14.080
not leaving until I feel like I at

00:03:11.599 --> 00:03:15.599
least hit almost every single one

00:03:14.080 --> 00:03:18.480
of these, even if it's just for a couple

00:03:18.480 --> 00:03:22.640
of

00:03:22.640 --> 00:03:27.119
minutes."I

00:03:29.040 --> 00:03:31.840
didn't know how to really handle it

00:03:30.720 --> 00:03:34.159
because

00:03:31.840 --> 00:03:37.519
I've never been

00:03:34.159 --> 00:03:40.319
given that option. So as I was

00:03:37.519 --> 00:03:42.720
looking into this and I

00:03:40.319 --> 00:03:45.040
jumped into the portal, I could see the

00:03:42.720 --> 00:03:46.959
river of it and he said, "Flow in this."So

00:03:45.040 --> 00:03:51.359
I was praying. Then I started

00:03:46.959 --> 00:03:53.840
praying for the drones and 911

00:03:51.360 --> 00:03:57.439
distractions.

00:03:53.840 --> 00:03:59.599
I could see a plot from the enemy,

00:03:57.439 --> 00:04:03.599
and the Lord said, "This is not a

00:03:59.599 --> 00:04:06.560
terrorist attack. This is an act of war from

00:04:03.599 --> 00:04:09.518
what has infiltrated America."They

00:04:06.560 --> 00:04:11.760
are sleeper cells that are truly

00:04:09.519 --> 00:04:14.319
hidden. They're sleeping, and you're

00:04:11.760 --> 00:04:17.839
not going to hear internet chatter of

00:04:14.319 --> 00:04:19.839
some ISIS enthusiast going, "Hey, we're

00:04:17.839 --> 00:04:21.440
going to do this and

00:04:19.839 --> 00:04:23.198
that."The

00:04:23.199 --> 00:04:28.160
Lord was showing me, he said,

00:04:25.600 --> 00:04:30.960
"These are trained soldiers. There's no

00:04:28.160 --> 00:04:33.600
chatter. What you are hearing is that

00:04:30.960 --> 00:04:36.400
secret signal

00:04:33.600 --> 00:04:40.240
that is like a Morse code

00:04:36.400 --> 00:04:43.599
that is only broadcast at certain times of

00:04:40.240 --> 00:04:45.040
day, once a week or once a

00:04:43.600 --> 00:04:47.440
month."It

00:04:45.040 --> 00:04:51.280
was coming from a

00:04:47.440 --> 00:04:53.520
signal and it sounded like

00:04:51.280 --> 00:04:55.758
the little thing you push the button on

00:04:53.520 --> 00:04:58.320
the Speak & Spell. Do you remember

00:04:55.759 --> 00:05:01.280
Speak & Spell in the '80s? It sounded

00:04:58.320 --> 00:05:04.560
like a voice, like Speak & Spell. And I

00:05:01.280 --> 00:05:08.479
could hear the numbers and

00:05:04.560 --> 00:05:11.039
it was a deciphered code.

00:05:08.479 --> 00:05:14.320
It was the deciphered code that was

00:05:11.039 --> 00:05:16.800
coming to the soldiers, the enemy

00:05:14.320 --> 00:05:18.240
within, the Red Dawn experience that I

00:05:16.800 --> 00:05:19.919
keep telling y'all about all the time. I

00:05:18.240 --> 00:05:21.840
say we got to pray against the Red Dawn

00:05:19.919 --> 00:05:24.960
experience. We got to pray against the

00:05:21.840 --> 00:05:27.758
enemy within. This is an infiltration of

00:05:24.960 --> 00:05:29.120
the enemy that is not terrorists. I

00:05:27.759 --> 00:05:30.800
would say, like I said, it's an act of

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:33.600
war. These are trained soldiers and they

00:05:30.800 --> 00:05:35.919
look like Special Ops. But I was praying

00:05:33.600 --> 00:05:38.320
into this and I heard the Speak &

00:05:35.919 --> 00:05:40.000
Spell sound. It was a voice. But as they

00:05:38.320 --> 00:05:41.919
would get the code, it would only last

00:05:40.000 --> 00:05:44.960
for a couple of seconds, but they knew when

00:05:41.919 --> 00:05:48.479
to get the code of when they were to be

00:05:44.960 --> 00:05:50.638
commissioned to do it, like

00:05:48.479 --> 00:05:52.639
"stand down"or "go ahead."It

00:05:50.639 --> 00:05:54.400
was a

00:05:52.639 --> 00:05:56.639
code and they would have to write down

00:05:54.400 --> 00:05:58.799
the numbers and then they would decipher

00:05:56.639 --> 00:06:01.440
it with the deciphering

00:05:58.800 --> 00:06:02.720
sheet. So I saw it was very

00:06:01.440 --> 00:06:05.919
well thought out. And the Lord said

00:06:02.720 --> 00:06:07.280
they're not using the internet.

00:06:07.280 --> 00:06:12.559
They're using a different means, like

00:06:09.199 --> 00:06:15.600
Cold War old communications.

00:06:12.560 --> 00:06:18.000
So I saw it. So they were listening for

00:06:15.600 --> 00:06:21.360
their code.

00:06:18.000 --> 00:06:25.360
Then I saw drones and the Lord was

00:06:21.360 --> 00:06:28.319
showing me 911 distractions.

00:06:25.360 --> 00:06:31.840
I saw that they would

00:06:28.319 --> 00:06:33.520
try in the days ahead to create an

00:06:31.840 --> 00:06:36.000
event

00:06:33.520 --> 00:06:38.240
to make all the police go over

00:06:36.000 --> 00:06:40.720
there. You make a little event happen

00:06:38.240 --> 00:06:43.680
over here so they think it's a

00:06:40.720 --> 00:06:46.000
major event, and all the law

00:06:43.680 --> 00:06:47.680
enforcement would flood to this area

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:51.120
because they think, "Oh, this is

00:06:47.680 --> 00:06:53.759
the big thing."But the

00:06:51.120 --> 00:06:55.759
big thing was down the road.

00:06:57.440 --> 00:07:04.800
So I saw a planned thing

00:07:01.360 --> 00:07:09.919
to disrupt 911

00:07:04.800 --> 00:07:11.919
services to distract from the

00:07:09.919 --> 00:07:15.680
main event.

00:07:11.919 --> 00:07:18.639
I saw a hospital in Boston. I saw a Red

00:07:15.680 --> 00:07:20.319
Cross. I saw a Red Cross on this. It

00:07:18.639 --> 00:07:23.199
looked like something on the medical

00:07:20.319 --> 00:07:25.039
ship for the Navy. It was a big Red

00:07:23.199 --> 00:07:27.840
Cross. I don't know if this is type and

00:07:25.039 --> 00:07:29.120
shadow metaphor or whatever, but because

00:07:27.840 --> 00:07:30.638
sometimes it is when the Lord's showing

00:07:29.120 --> 00:07:33.039
me stuff. It's not always just black and

00:07:30.639 --> 00:07:34.960
white. It's like the

00:07:33.039 --> 00:07:36.880
seven

00:07:34.960 --> 00:07:38.400
fat cows and seven skinny cows.

00:07:36.880 --> 00:07:39.680
When you're looking at it, it doesn't

00:07:38.400 --> 00:07:41.599
mean anything about the cows; it means

00:07:39.680 --> 00:07:43.280
famine's coming and seven years of

00:07:41.599 --> 00:07:44.560
blessing and seven years of famine.

00:07:49.280 --> 00:07:53.758
So I see

00:07:52.080 --> 00:07:56.000
the building and the Lord said,

00:07:53.759 --> 00:07:58.560
"Look at the hospital."But

00:07:56.000 --> 00:08:00.720
I could see snipers on the top of

00:07:58.560 --> 00:08:04.000
certain buildings trying to take out law

00:08:00.720 --> 00:08:07.120
enforcement when they came, hiding on top

00:08:04.000 --> 00:08:08.720
of buildings in black outfits. And they

00:08:07.120 --> 00:08:11.360
were trying to not just get police

00:08:08.720 --> 00:08:14.319
officers, but firefighters. And the Lord

00:08:11.360 --> 00:08:16.319
said, "Pray for the firefighters. Pray

00:08:14.319 --> 00:08:18.800
for your law enforcement. Pray for the

00:08:16.319 --> 00:08:20.479
FBI. Pray for Homeland Security."That's

00:08:18.800 --> 00:08:22.240
why I was praying

00:08:30.240 --> 00:08:34.959
over all your law enforcement.

00:08:31.520 --> 00:08:37.519
Pray over New Orleans,

00:08:37.519 --> 00:08:43.760
Nashville, and Boston. They were

00:08:40.479 --> 00:08:45.920
in a line: Boston,

00:08:43.760 --> 00:08:49.519
Nashville, and New Orleans—the

00:08:45.920 --> 00:08:52.240
furthest south, mid, and

00:08:49.519 --> 00:08:53.920
north. I thought it was interesting.

00:08:52.240 --> 00:08:57.519
But the way He had me praying over

00:08:53.920 --> 00:09:01.839
three cities—Minneapolis;

00:08:57.519 --> 00:09:04.720
Omaha, Nebraska; and

00:09:01.839 --> 00:09:08.959
these cities where they have cells

00:09:04.720 --> 00:09:12.160
of these people in them—I

00:09:08.959 --> 00:09:17.040
was praying over that. Then

00:09:12.160 --> 00:09:20.319
I was shown the Boston Red Sox and the New York

00:09:17.040 --> 00:09:22.880
Yankees. I don't know why; I saw the

00:09:20.320 --> 00:09:25.279
stadiums and was praying over these

00:09:22.880 --> 00:09:28.000
two rivals. Pray over the games; pray

00:09:25.279 --> 00:09:30.160
over baseball in the days ahead.

00:09:28.000 --> 00:09:32.000
Just pray over baseball, America's

00:09:30.160 --> 00:09:33.680
pastime. They always call it

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:35.600
America's pastime,

00:09:33.680 --> 00:09:37.920
right? I still love baseball; baseball

00:09:35.600 --> 00:09:42.640
is amazing to me. I love the playoffs;

00:09:37.920 --> 00:09:45.680
it's my thing. But

00:09:42.640 --> 00:09:50.080
praying over our baseball games, over Judge.

00:09:45.680 --> 00:09:52.719
I saw Judge's

00:09:50.080 --> 00:09:55.360
face in the Yankees. I saw him

00:09:52.720 --> 00:09:57.200
and I don't know why, but I knew it

00:09:55.360 --> 00:10:01.440
was the Yankees. Then praying over

00:09:57.200 --> 00:10:03.760
the World Cup with the Mexican team,

00:10:01.440 --> 00:10:07.040
Mexico, with the green and white

00:10:03.760 --> 00:10:10.160
jerseys, praying over this.

00:10:07.040 --> 00:10:13.160
I saw them; I saw the World Cup. I saw

00:10:13.279 --> 00:10:21.600
the drones. The drones had a

00:10:17.600 --> 00:10:23.920
bubble around them. It was an electric

00:10:21.600 --> 00:10:26.720
bubble that looked like one of those

00:10:23.920 --> 00:10:28.640
balls you touch

00:10:26.720 --> 00:10:30.399
at a science fair where

00:10:28.640 --> 00:10:34.000
the electricity touches your

00:10:30.399 --> 00:10:38.640
finger. It had a force field around it.

00:10:34.000 --> 00:10:41.279
The drones had a thin membrane

00:10:38.640 --> 00:10:44.800
that looked like a force field with

00:10:41.279 --> 00:10:47.839
electricity beams going all around it.

00:10:44.800 --> 00:10:50.640
And as you would use a jammer to knock

00:10:47.839 --> 00:10:53.279
it down—I saw our law enforcement had

00:10:50.640 --> 00:10:55.439
jammers that look like little guns, like

00:10:53.279 --> 00:10:59.200
little razor things—but they

00:10:55.440 --> 00:11:02.560
couldn't. They had a mathematical

00:10:59.200 --> 00:11:05.440
equation. It was a mathematical code

00:11:02.560 --> 00:11:08.239
that you had to penetrate with something like

00:11:05.440 --> 00:11:10.240
a virus.

00:11:08.240 --> 00:11:12.640
Excuse my ignorance, but this is all

00:11:10.240 --> 00:11:14.160
I know how to do to describe to you what I

00:11:12.640 --> 00:11:17.199
was seeing in the spirit. They

00:11:14.160 --> 00:11:19.760
needed a virus to break the code; they

00:11:17.200 --> 00:11:22.800
needed something to break the cipher of

00:11:19.760 --> 00:11:26.160
the bubble that protects the

00:11:22.800 --> 00:11:29.599
drone. I saw all these drones had

00:11:26.160 --> 00:11:32.000
big wings, four of them.

00:11:29.600 --> 00:11:34.640
They had a payload, a white box

00:11:32.000 --> 00:11:37.600
underneath the drone, and

00:11:34.640 --> 00:11:39.360
the Lord said, 'This is a

00:11:37.600 --> 00:11:42.320
payload.'So

00:11:39.360 --> 00:11:45.120
I saw that and I saw the drones being

00:11:42.320 --> 00:11:48.720
used, but they have come out with a

00:11:45.120 --> 00:11:51.440
frequency to jam the jammers so that

00:11:48.720 --> 00:11:53.519
they don't take them down. It

00:11:51.440 --> 00:11:56.399
was, like I said, a mathematical

00:11:53.519 --> 00:11:58.399
code.

00:11:58.399 --> 00:12:01.279
I don't know what I'm

00:11:59.680 --> 00:12:03.199
saying; I'm just telling you what I saw. I'm

00:12:01.279 --> 00:12:05.519
telling it to you, Brandon.

00:12:03.200 --> 00:12:07.040
This is all like rocket science

00:12:05.519 --> 00:12:09.040
to me. I'm just trying to tell you what

00:12:07.040 --> 00:12:10.480
the Lord was showing me.

00:12:09.040 --> 00:12:13.040
I thought it was very interesting

00:12:10.480 --> 00:12:15.200
because I saw the bubble around these

00:12:13.040 --> 00:12:18.319
things. They were trying to plan

00:12:18.320 --> 00:12:24.800
a swarm, like bees,

00:12:22.160 --> 00:12:28.639
to all come out. It's too much—what

00:12:24.800 --> 00:12:30.240
do you do with a swarm? It

00:12:28.639 --> 00:12:34.480
was

00:12:30.240 --> 00:12:37.440
very dark.

00:12:34.480 --> 00:12:42.079
As I was looking into New Orleans, I

00:12:37.440 --> 00:12:46.000
heard 'Bay of Pigs'again. I saw the fox

00:12:42.079 --> 00:12:47.920
in the Bay of Pigs area look towards New

00:12:46.000 --> 00:12:50.079
Orleans.

00:12:47.920 --> 00:12:53.279
The Lord said, 'Pray over New

00:12:50.079 --> 00:12:55.120
Orleans. Pray over this.'So, I'm seeing in

00:12:53.279 --> 00:12:57.120
part; we'll see if

00:12:55.120 --> 00:12:59.680
God gives us any more today.

00:12:57.120 --> 00:13:02.959
It isn't about us. We attract

00:12:59.680 --> 00:13:05.839
to deflect. We keep our eyes on Jesus.

00:13:02.959 --> 00:13:08.560
It's so important that we

00:13:05.839 --> 00:13:11.360
decrease and He increase, that no matter

00:13:08.560 --> 00:13:13.119
how much we see or what God shows us, we

00:13:11.360 --> 00:13:15.040
keep the main thing the main thing, and

00:13:13.120 --> 00:13:17.200
it's Him. It's all about Him, and it

00:13:15.040 --> 00:13:18.959
will continue to be about Him. It's not

00:13:17.200 --> 00:13:20.880
about Brandon Biggs, my

00:13:18.959 --> 00:13:23.040
wife, or my son. It's always about

00:13:20.880 --> 00:13:24.480
giving God glory for using us in these

00:13:23.040 --> 00:13:27.839
last days because He could use any one

00:13:24.480 --> 00:13:30.240
of you. It's to keep humble.

00:13:27.839 --> 00:13:32.399
He rebuked me even; sometimes

00:13:30.240 --> 00:13:33.600
people want to talk to you,

00:13:32.399 --> 00:13:34.800
and I go, 'Lord, why do they want

00:13:33.600 --> 00:13:36.560
to bother me?'I

00:13:34.800 --> 00:13:38.160
think I'm just a real private

00:13:36.560 --> 00:13:39.359
person; I kind of stay to myself. He

00:13:38.160 --> 00:13:43.160
said, 'Brandon, what makes you think

00:13:39.360 --> 00:13:43.160
they want to talk to you?'I

00:13:45.279 --> 00:13:49.279
said, 'Well, they're the ones

00:13:46.639 --> 00:13:50.800
talking to me.'He said, 'It's Christ in

00:13:49.279 --> 00:13:52.560
you.

00:13:50.800 --> 00:13:54.479
They see Jesus; they see Me in you,

00:13:52.560 --> 00:13:56.479
Son.

00:13:54.480 --> 00:13:58.480
They're pulling from the anointing.

00:13:56.480 --> 00:14:00.480
It's not you

00:13:58.480 --> 00:14:02.079
they're after; they want the glory; they

00:14:00.480 --> 00:14:04.959
want the anointing. They sense

00:14:02.079 --> 00:14:07.359
something, and that's why they're coming.'But

00:14:04.959 --> 00:14:08.959
it's not you. Anytime you start

00:14:07.360 --> 00:14:10.800
thinking it's you—'Why do they want to

00:14:08.959 --> 00:14:12.880
talk to me?'—well, they don't want

00:14:10.800 --> 00:14:14.880
to talk to you. What makes you think

00:14:12.880 --> 00:14:17.040
they do?

00:14:14.880 --> 00:14:18.639
I repented immediately. He said, 'There

00:14:17.040 --> 00:14:21.279
goes a root that can turn

00:14:18.639 --> 00:14:24.880
into a root of pride real quick. Let it die.'I

00:14:21.279 --> 00:14:28.079
said, 'Yes, Lord.'It's

00:14:24.880 --> 00:14:31.920
always staying on that

00:14:28.079 --> 00:14:36.079
line, staying in that balance

00:14:31.920 --> 00:14:40.160
of where He's at, staying on the

00:14:36.079 --> 00:14:44.239
life source, that you are always

00:14:40.160 --> 00:14:46.319
decreasing. You attract to deflect.

00:14:44.240 --> 00:14:47.360
You attract to deflect even in your

00:14:46.320 --> 00:14:48.480
thoughts.

00:14:47.360 --> 00:14:49.839
'Why do they want to talk to me?

00:14:48.480 --> 00:14:52.480
Why do they want to bother me?'They

00:14:49.839 --> 00:14:54.880
don't. They're after the anointing. They

00:14:52.480 --> 00:14:56.399
need a touch from Jesus.

00:14:54.880 --> 00:14:58.480
Every single one of them, even if they see a

00:14:56.399 --> 00:14:59.920
mirror, they see Jesus in you. Because

00:14:58.480 --> 00:15:01.839
in the days ahead—this is where I'm

00:14:59.920 --> 00:15:04.639
going with this—there'll

00:15:01.839 --> 00:15:08.079
be a lot of

00:15:04.639 --> 00:15:10.880
you that are going to be the

00:15:08.079 --> 00:15:13.680
catchers. The pitcher is going to throw it

00:15:10.880 --> 00:15:15.839
hot; you're going to get a fastball.

00:15:13.680 --> 00:15:18.000
When they're

00:15:15.839 --> 00:15:19.519
coming into the body of Christ—these

00:15:18.000 --> 00:15:21.519
sinners,

00:15:19.519 --> 00:15:23.360
the unsaved, the

00:15:21.519 --> 00:15:26.240
people who need to get Jesus—they're

00:15:23.360 --> 00:15:27.440
coming in hot.

00:15:27.440 --> 00:15:31.279
I'm trying to describe how I saw it in the vision.

00:15:29.120 --> 00:15:33.440
The Lord said, 'You're catching. Are you

00:15:31.279 --> 00:15:36.560
ready? Do you have your mitts ready? Are

00:15:33.440 --> 00:15:40.160
you ready to receive the people that are coming?'Be

00:15:36.560 --> 00:15:41.839
patient with my babies.

00:15:40.160 --> 00:15:44.160
There will be many of you that walk with

00:15:41.839 --> 00:15:46.399
the glory on you. There'll be many of

00:15:44.160 --> 00:15:48.480
you that walk with the presence of God,

00:15:46.399 --> 00:15:50.000
with healings and signs and wonders in

00:15:48.480 --> 00:15:54.279
these last days. For the harvest is

00:15:50.000 --> 00:15:54.279
plentiful and the laborers are few.

00:15:56.160 --> 00:16:02.319
Always attract to deflect.

00:16:00.480 --> 00:16:06.079
Give Him glory for everything you're

00:16:02.320 --> 00:16:09.519
about to see.

00:16:06.079 --> 00:16:11.599
It's all about Jesus all the time.

00:16:09.519 --> 00:16:13.680
It's so important. I listen

00:16:11.600 --> 00:16:15.519
to Kathryn Kuhlman all the time.

00:16:13.680 --> 00:16:17.599
I thought, 'Man, this lady is

00:16:15.519 --> 00:16:20.320
really dramatic,'but

00:16:17.600 --> 00:16:23.519
when you feel that you've

00:16:20.320 --> 00:16:25.519
grieved the Holy Spirit—like I did

00:16:23.519 --> 00:16:27.120
last night with some thoughts I had—the

00:16:25.519 --> 00:16:31.279
Lord corrects me.

00:16:27.120 --> 00:16:34.000
I walk a very thin line; to whom much

00:16:31.279 --> 00:16:36.880
is given, much is required.

00:16:36.880 --> 00:16:42.000
I always check my thermostat.

00:16:40.240 --> 00:16:44.079
Where are you with your walk with

00:16:42.000 --> 00:16:45.839
the Lord today?

00:16:48.639 --> 00:16:53.040
Have you checked your spiritual thermostat

00:16:50.399 --> 00:16:55.519
today? Where were you when

00:16:53.040 --> 00:16:58.079
you woke up? I had to go back and look

00:16:55.519 --> 00:16:59.360
at all the mercy scriptures. I look at

00:16:58.079 --> 00:17:04.079
all the times I think, 'Well, God's mad

00:16:59.360 --> 00:17:07.520
at me; He's upset.'And He said, 'Brandon,

00:17:04.079 --> 00:17:11.760
go look at all my mercy scriptures.

00:17:07.520 --> 00:17:16.559
Go meditate on mercy today.

00:17:11.760 --> 00:17:19.280
How much do I love you?'I said, 'Yeah,

00:17:16.559 --> 00:17:22.280
His goodness and His

00:17:19.280 --> 00:17:22.280
mercy.'Even

00:17:27.119 --> 00:17:32.799
when

00:17:29.120 --> 00:17:38.399
you get off track and He checks your

00:17:32.799 --> 00:17:40.799
heart, you think, 'Oh,

00:17:38.400 --> 00:17:45.360
I don't want to mess up. I want to keep

00:17:40.799 --> 00:17:47.662
right with You.'But He shows me He has

00:17:45.360 --> 00:17:49.681
mercy.

00:17:50.400 --> 00:17:54.120
God loves you.

00:17:57.280 --> 00:18:00.639
I don't even know why I'm

00:17:58.160 --> 00:18:02.880
crying. It hit me hard.

00:18:00.640 --> 00:18:06.880
I told Diana, 'We have to go

00:18:02.880 --> 00:18:09.120
drive around for a little bit,'because

00:18:06.880 --> 00:18:12.000
that's where I worship, in my

00:18:09.120 --> 00:18:13.120
car, and I drive and pray over the city.

00:18:12.000 --> 00:18:15.679
In the middle of the night, I said,

00:18:13.120 --> 00:18:18.799
'Let's go. I want to drive and pray.'I'm

00:18:15.679 --> 00:18:20.240
going over all the

00:18:18.799 --> 00:18:22.559
things that He's talking to me about regarding

00:18:20.240 --> 00:18:25.520
the end times. And I

00:18:22.559 --> 00:18:28.080
always keep my thermostat hot.

00:18:25.520 --> 00:18:30.080
I try really hard,

00:18:28.080 --> 00:18:32.159
but even whenever he tells me, "Read

00:18:30.080 --> 00:18:34.399
these scriptures about mercy today."What

00:18:32.160 --> 00:18:37.120
are you going

00:18:34.400 --> 00:18:38.720
through? Find scriptures that pertain to

00:18:37.120 --> 00:18:41.840
what you're going through and meditate

00:18:38.720 --> 00:18:45.360
on them. And today I

00:18:41.840 --> 00:18:47.600
needed mercy. Today I

00:18:45.360 --> 00:18:48.959
said, "God,

00:18:47.600 --> 00:18:50.480
you know, I feel like you're

00:18:48.960 --> 00:18:52.320
irritated at me or whatever."And you

00:18:50.480 --> 00:18:54.000
know, correction comes. Correction is

00:18:52.320 --> 00:18:56.240
not always fun when he corrects you.

00:18:54.000 --> 00:18:57.840
It's a spanking. And at the same time,

00:18:56.240 --> 00:19:01.023
you go, "Are we cool? Can we

00:18:57.840 --> 00:19:02.639
fist bump? Are we all right?"And of

00:19:01.023 --> 00:19:04.959
course we're right. But

00:19:02.640 --> 00:19:07.919
he said, "Oh, Brandon, meditate

00:19:04.960 --> 00:19:10.960
on my mercy towards you. Meditate on my

00:19:07.919 --> 00:19:14.559
love towards you today.

00:19:10.960 --> 00:19:17.120
Get rid of the stinking thinking.

00:19:14.559 --> 00:19:18.720
I'm not mad at you. I have

00:19:17.120 --> 00:19:21.039
longsuffering.

00:19:18.720 --> 00:19:23.919
I love you. I love your wife. I love

00:19:21.039 --> 00:19:25.520
your kids. I correct those I

00:19:23.919 --> 00:19:29.039
love."And

00:19:25.520 --> 00:19:31.520
correction makes the bridle of the horse's

00:19:29.039 --> 00:19:33.200
mouth go. And the

00:19:31.520 --> 00:19:34.960
more you're broken, the

00:19:33.200 --> 00:19:37.600
less he has to jerk on that bridle

00:19:34.960 --> 00:19:39.440
to get you to move. If you have

00:19:37.600 --> 00:19:42.799
to yank a horse, that horse is in

00:19:39.440 --> 00:19:44.720
rebellion; a horse just has to be led.

00:19:42.799 --> 00:19:46.559
And the more you just barely do that,

00:19:44.720 --> 00:19:49.679
the horse will move. It doesn't have

00:19:46.559 --> 00:19:51.039
to take a hard pull

00:19:49.679 --> 00:19:53.120
unless the horse is not doing what you

00:19:51.039 --> 00:19:55.200
tell it to do. But you just barely lead

00:19:53.120 --> 00:19:58.879
that horse and that horse will just go and

00:19:55.200 --> 00:20:01.760
run.

00:19:58.880 --> 00:20:04.640
It doesn't take much. And that's when

00:20:01.760 --> 00:20:07.280
you're pliable.

00:20:04.640 --> 00:20:09.520
God will do the exceedingly abundantly

00:20:07.280 --> 00:20:12.240
above all that you dare ask or think. If

00:20:09.520 --> 00:20:13.760
you're pliable in your life and

00:20:12.240 --> 00:20:17.714
keeping him the main thing,

00:20:13.760 --> 00:20:17.714
keeping my eyes on him,

00:20:17.760 --> 00:20:23.760
you have to yield

00:20:19.440 --> 00:20:25.039
yourself to him every day.

00:20:23.760 --> 00:20:26.400
I just thought it was

00:20:25.039 --> 00:20:27.679
interesting some of the things that I'm

00:20:26.400 --> 00:20:29.760
going through and just how he's teaching

00:20:27.679 --> 00:20:31.520
me and

00:20:31.520 --> 00:20:34.080
standing against the things that have

00:20:32.640 --> 00:20:36.960
been trying to come against me in the

00:20:34.080 --> 00:20:39.439
spirit realm and learning the authority

00:20:36.960 --> 00:20:41.120
of the believer. You can hear

00:20:39.440 --> 00:20:42.400
Sister Billye Brim talk about the

00:20:41.120 --> 00:20:44.158
authority of the believer, Pastor

00:20:42.400 --> 00:20:46.320
Candace,

00:20:44.159 --> 00:20:48.480
but you can parrot

00:20:46.320 --> 00:20:51.360
it really easy.

00:20:48.480 --> 00:20:52.960
You can be a parrot and just quote

00:20:51.360 --> 00:20:54.879
Sister Billye's book, "The Authority of

00:20:52.960 --> 00:20:57.360
the Believer,"and Brother Hagin, and you

00:20:54.880 --> 00:21:00.080
can read that and go, "Yeah, I've

00:20:57.360 --> 00:21:02.399
got the authority of the believer. Of

00:21:00.080 --> 00:21:04.639
course I do. Yeah, that's right, pastor.

00:21:02.400 --> 00:21:07.200
High five."And you can be all excited

00:21:04.640 --> 00:21:10.400
about it. But when the enemy comes and

00:21:07.200 --> 00:21:11.679
the roaring lion comes at your house and

00:21:10.400 --> 00:21:14.799
you're sitting there and they're not

00:21:11.679 --> 00:21:17.600
there, the book is a couple feet

00:21:14.799 --> 00:21:18.879
away and you know the enemy is

00:21:17.600 --> 00:21:21.120
there and he's knocking at your door. I

00:21:18.880 --> 00:21:23.159
heard an

00:21:21.120 --> 00:21:24.080
audible voice

00:21:23.159 --> 00:21:26.080
saying, "I'm

00:21:24.080 --> 00:21:28.240
mad about yesterday and what we did

00:21:28.240 --> 00:21:31.840
yesterday."I

00:21:31.840 --> 00:21:35.199
stopped and I started praying in

00:21:33.679 --> 00:21:38.240
the spirit and the Lord said, "Stand

00:21:35.200 --> 00:21:40.080
against this."I

00:21:38.240 --> 00:21:42.080
get the word down and I quote it out of

00:21:40.080 --> 00:21:45.280
my mouth, but I don't want to parrot

00:21:42.080 --> 00:21:47.678
something that I've heard from

00:21:45.280 --> 00:21:50.158
somebody else. I want it to be a Rhema to

00:21:47.679 --> 00:21:52.080
me. And the only way

00:21:50.159 --> 00:21:54.480
you're going to get Rhema is by you

00:21:52.080 --> 00:21:55.840
meditating on the word. You're going to

00:21:54.480 --> 00:21:57.360
have to get Ephesians down in your

00:21:55.840 --> 00:22:00.399
heart. You're going to have to get

00:21:57.360 --> 00:22:02.639
the Bible

00:22:00.400 --> 00:22:04.480
and you read

00:22:02.640 --> 00:22:06.640
it and you meditate on it and you apply it

00:22:04.480 --> 00:22:08.720
and you get the supplements like "The

00:22:06.640 --> 00:22:10.240
Authority of the Believer"and you read

00:22:08.720 --> 00:22:12.640
that and you apply it.

00:22:10.240 --> 00:22:15.440
At the entrance of his

00:22:12.640 --> 00:22:17.679
word brings forth light. And the more you

00:22:15.440 --> 00:22:19.440
get that word down inside your heart, the

00:22:17.679 --> 00:22:21.120
more you get it coming

00:22:19.440 --> 00:22:23.760
through your eyes, it will renew

00:22:21.120 --> 00:22:27.280
your mind and then you'll realize, "This

00:22:23.760 --> 00:22:29.600
isn't me parroting a word

00:22:27.280 --> 00:22:32.000
and a book anymore. This is becoming a Rhema

00:22:29.600 --> 00:22:34.559
word to my spirit and it

00:22:32.000 --> 00:22:37.360
has power and authority."When

00:22:34.559 --> 00:22:38.960
a word becomes Rhema to you,

00:22:37.360 --> 00:22:41.439
power and authority will come out

00:22:38.960 --> 00:22:43.280
of you. So the more you meditate on

00:22:41.440 --> 00:22:45.039
the word, the more you get it down

00:22:43.280 --> 00:22:47.200
inside your heart, you're not just parroting

00:22:45.039 --> 00:22:49.620
what your pastor's saying.

00:22:47.200 --> 00:22:50.480
I really want to encourage you.

00:22:50.480 --> 00:22:54.799
It starts with parroting. It's like

00:22:52.720 --> 00:22:58.159
babies. They imitate their mom and

00:22:54.799 --> 00:23:01.200
daddies. Be imitators of God as

00:22:58.159 --> 00:23:03.200
dear children imitate their fathers. So

00:23:01.200 --> 00:23:04.720
imitate the Lord. But the only way

00:23:03.200 --> 00:23:07.120
you're going to do that is by watching

00:23:04.720 --> 00:23:09.360
and looking at him

00:23:07.120 --> 00:23:12.639
by mirroring that. This is

00:23:09.360 --> 00:23:16.000
God speaking to me.

00:23:12.640 --> 00:23:17.919
The word is alive and it is

00:23:16.000 --> 00:23:19.679
written for you to get that down inside

00:23:17.919 --> 00:23:22.720
of you. If you want to know who God

00:23:19.679 --> 00:23:24.640
is, read this Bible.

00:23:22.720 --> 00:23:26.000
When you get

00:23:24.640 --> 00:23:30.286
that word inside of you, it will change

00:23:26.000 --> 00:23:30.286
you from the inside out.

00:23:30.799 --> 00:23:34.320
The entrance of his word brings

00:23:32.320 --> 00:23:35.520
forth light. So I'm trying to help

00:23:34.320 --> 00:23:37.360
you because there's so many new

00:23:35.520 --> 00:23:38.879
believers that come on here and a lot of

00:23:37.360 --> 00:23:41.439
people that don't know anything about the

00:23:38.880 --> 00:23:44.240
word and they want to know, "Why am I still

00:23:41.440 --> 00:23:46.720
bound? Why am I broke? Why am I not

00:23:44.240 --> 00:23:48.720
making it financially? How come I'm

00:23:46.720 --> 00:23:50.960
not making it with my health?

00:23:48.720 --> 00:23:52.799
My marriage is a wreck and I'm

00:23:50.960 --> 00:23:55.360
strung out on drugs; I can't

00:23:52.799 --> 00:23:57.520
get free from that."You

00:23:55.360 --> 00:24:00.158
will know the truth and the truth will

00:23:57.520 --> 00:24:01.760
set you free. I have so many

00:24:00.159 --> 00:24:03.200
people say, "I need to have demons cast

00:24:01.760 --> 00:24:05.360
out of me."Yeah,

00:24:03.200 --> 00:24:06.960
you might. But the

00:24:05.360 --> 00:24:08.879
only way you're going to remain free,

00:24:06.960 --> 00:24:10.880
even if you got them cast out of you, is

00:24:08.880 --> 00:24:12.559
getting this word of God inside of you.

00:24:10.880 --> 00:24:14.559
Or he's going to bring eight more of his

00:24:12.559 --> 00:24:16.240
friends with him. They're going to bring

00:24:14.559 --> 00:24:17.918
a bunch of his little buddies and

00:24:16.240 --> 00:24:19.200
they're going to say, "Hey, we can go in there,"because he doesn't

00:24:17.919 --> 00:24:22.080
have the word

00:24:19.200 --> 00:24:23.919
inside of him still.

00:24:22.080 --> 00:24:26.399
The only way that you're going to stay

00:24:23.919 --> 00:24:30.279
free is getting a foundation of the word

00:24:26.400 --> 00:24:30.279
of God inside of you.

00:24:34.080 --> 00:24:39.199
You can quote scripture, but

00:24:37.600 --> 00:24:41.520
until it is real to you, it's like

00:24:39.200 --> 00:24:42.960
saying "Twinkle, Twinkle, Little Star."You

00:24:41.520 --> 00:24:45.760
can quote things out of your mouth and

00:24:42.960 --> 00:24:48.177
parrot things. But the enemy

00:24:48.177 --> 00:24:52.879
knows when you know. When

00:24:50.320 --> 00:24:56.080
you submit yourself therefore unto God,

00:24:52.880 --> 00:24:58.640
you resist the devil and he will flee.

00:24:56.080 --> 00:25:02.080
He knows when you know.

00:24:58.640 --> 00:25:04.480
He's seeking whom he may devour.

00:25:02.080 --> 00:25:06.000
Who can he devour? The one that doesn't

00:25:04.480 --> 00:25:08.240
have the word inside of their heart and

00:25:06.000 --> 00:25:10.320
is rooted and grounded in love.

00:25:08.240 --> 00:25:11.919
Faith works by love. So you've got to walk

00:25:10.320 --> 00:25:14.080
in love. You've got to check your love

00:25:11.919 --> 00:25:15.440
thermostat. So if your

00:25:14.080 --> 00:25:18.639
faith doesn't feel like it's working,

00:25:15.440 --> 00:25:20.320
check your love walk.

00:25:18.640 --> 00:25:21.360
How do you treat the people around you?

00:25:21.360 --> 00:25:24.080
Are

00:25:25.520 --> 00:25:30.158
you treating them cranky? Are you

00:25:27.120 --> 00:25:33.760
rude or hateful? God is love

00:25:30.159 --> 00:25:35.279
and the

00:25:33.760 --> 00:25:37.600
word of God will flow out of you when

00:25:35.279 --> 00:25:40.240
you get

00:25:37.600 --> 00:25:42.959
rooted in love. Love

00:25:40.240 --> 00:25:45.679
has to be priority because faith works

00:25:42.960 --> 00:25:47.360
by love.

00:25:49.039 --> 00:25:51.440
I don't

00:25:50.080 --> 00:25:53.678
understand why I'm not having any

00:25:51.440 --> 00:25:56.159
breakthrough?

00:25:53.679 --> 00:25:58.960
Check your love walk.

00:25:56.159 --> 00:26:00.640
Check how you treat people.

00:25:58.960 --> 00:26:04.080
Love takes no account of a suffered

00:26:00.640 --> 00:26:07.440
wrong. Love is not fretful. Love is not

00:26:04.080 --> 00:26:09.398
resentful. 1 Corinthians 13, I

00:26:07.440 --> 00:26:13.440
believe it is.

00:26:09.398 --> 00:26:15.600
Read it.

00:26:13.440 --> 00:26:18.240
Get love down inside of you. Love

00:26:15.600 --> 00:26:19.678
never fails. I'm

00:26:18.240 --> 00:26:22.480
trying to tell you all this because of

00:26:19.679 --> 00:26:24.240
